SUMMARY:Tesla Owners at the British Motor Show 2026
DESCRIPTION:Tesla Owners UK is delighted to have been invited to have a clu
 b stand at the British Motor Show at the Farnborough airport exhibition ce
 ntre (where previous everything electric shows have been held). We will be
  shortly inviting TOUK members to register if they wish to display their c
 ar at the event for 1\, 2 or the full 3 days\, and our exhibitors will get
  a free pass (worth up to £80) for their car and driver to enjoy the show.
  And of course your display car will mean you are parked up in the middle 
 of the action! We are looking for owners who will be able to spend a coupl
 e of hours on the stand to talk about all things Tesla and electric drivin
 g. You can enjoy the rest of the show in between your volunteering spot. T
 his is the first time we will be taking part in this show so we hope to pu
 t on a great display and a chance to show off your car.\n\nListing: August
  21st–23rd\, 2026\n\nWall clock / source TZ: Europe/London\n\nEvent & tick
 ets (Ti.to): https://ti.to/teslaownersuk/tesla-owners-at-the-british-motor
 -show-2026\n\nSource list: upcoming\n\nTi.to DTSTAMP: 2026-07-15T10:47:13+
 00:00\n\nTesla Owners UK: https://ti.to/teslaownersuk\n\nClub site: https:
 //teslaowners.uk/
